2. Extracted captureSessionFileFence() helper for fence snapshot logic
3. releaseHeldLockWithFence() captures fence even when no lock is held
4. reacquireAfterPrompt() verifies fence without re-acquiring the lock — each write uses withSessionWriteLock for independent acquire/release

